 + Techs: Life on the Frontline is nurses, physician assistants, nurse practitioners, technologists, who work in cardiovascular care, cath labs, angiography suites, and endovascular operating rooms.\",\"84\":{\"114\":{\"type\":\"year\",\"enabled\":\"1\",\"fields\":{\"year\":\"2017\",\"hyperlink\":\"https:\\/\\/www.expobadge.com\\/certification\\/VIVA2017\"}}}}}', '2018-02-13 00:53:20', '2018-02-13 00:53:20', 'a7f3a6df-930e-40d3-a7dd-ad3aa2ece14b'),
