 VIVA Global Theater on Thursday, November 8.<\\/div>\",\"90\":[\"304\"]}}', '2018-03-02 14:07:29', '2018-03-02 14:07:29', 'd49bb0ac-68cc-4369-8d66-09ef56dd1ac6'),
